        {
            "id": 6260363,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 聯合健康保險(UNH-US)大漲5.01%，報340.81美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>聯合健康保險(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UNH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UNH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UNH-US</a>)截至台北時間04日04:45股價上漲16.27美元，報340.81美元，漲幅5.01%，成交量7,391,238（股），盤中最高價340.81美元、最低價325.01美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.95%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.39%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.32%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.79%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>聯合健康保險(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UNH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UNH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UNH-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-0.9%</li> <li>近 1 月：-3.13%</li> <li>近 3 月：+4.71%</li> <li>近 6 月：+6.11%</li> <li>今年以來：-35.91%</li></ul></section></main>",
